 put together test ROMs provide in terms of trying to increase the accuracy.  Hopefully along the way I gain some knowledge and help others do the same.  Isn't that what emulation is all about?  <br /><br /><img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /><br /><br />26 more test ROM challenges ahead...<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3705">cpow</a> — Thu Jul 08, 2010 11:07 pm</p><hr />
